io.grpc.util

Class MutableHandlerRegistry

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.grpc.HandlerRegistry
      • io.grpc.util.MutableHandlerRegistry

  • @ThreadSafe
 @ExperimentalApi(value="https://github.com/grpc/grpc-java/issues/933")
public final class MutableHandlerRegistry
extends HandlerRegistry
    Default implementation of MutableHandlerRegistry.

    Uses ConcurrentHashMap to avoid service registration excessively blocking method lookup.
